<title>UK: OPEC basket price fell to $17.71 on Friday.</title>
<headline>OPEC basket price fell to $17.71 on Friday.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-05-05</dateline>
<text>
<p>The price of OPEC's basket of seven crudes fell to $17.71 a barrel on Friday from $17.93 a barrel the previous day, according to the OPEC Secretariat's calculations, the OPEC news agency said on Monday.</p>
<p>The basket comprises Algeria's Saharan Blend, Indonesia's Minas, Nigeria's Bonny Light, Saudi Arabia's Arabian Light, Dubai of the UAE, Venezuela's Tia Juana and Mexico's Isthmus.</p>
